"On Microsoft Windows, messages are always sent to the Event Log using "
"the code <code>LOG_USER</code>."
msgstr ""
"Pada Microsoft Windows, pesan selalu dikirim ke Log Even menggunakan "
"kode <code>LOG_USER</code>."

