"Layout Builder can be selectively enabled on the \"Manage Display\" "
"page in the <a href=\":field_ui\">Field UI</a>. This allows you to "
"control the output of each type of display individually. For example, "
"a \"Basic page\" might have view modes such as Full and Teaser, with "
"each view mode having different layouts selected."
msgstr ""
"Layout Builder dapat diaktifkan secara selektif pada halaman \"Kelola "
"Tampilan\" di <a href=\":field_ui\">Field UI</a>. Ini memungkinkan "
"Anda mengontrol keluaran dari setiap jenis tampilan secara terpisah. "
"Misalnya, \"Halaman dasar\" mungkin memiliki mode tampilan seperti "
"Full dan Teaser, dengan setiap mode tampilan menggunakan tata letak "
"yang berbeda."

