"<span aria-hidden=\"true\">(-)</span> akan dipertahankan."

msgid ""
"Replace sequences of dots, underscores and/or dashes with the "
"replacement character"
msgstr ""
"Ganti rangkaian titik, garis bawah, dan/atau tanda hubung dengan "
"karakter pengganti"

