"Depending on the installed workflow type, additional configuration can "
"be available in the edit form of a workflow."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada jenis alur kerja yang terpasang, konfigurasi tambahan "
"dapat tersedia di formulir pengeditan alur kerja."

