msgstr "Memahami Hook | Drupal.org"

msgid "What Are Hooks? | Drupalize.me"
msgstr "Apa Itu Hook? | Drupalize.me"

msgid "This screencast walks through how to attach a webform to node."
msgstr "Screencast ini membahas cara melampirkan webform ke node."

