msgstr "Varian webform berhasil diperbarui."

msgid ""
"Select variants and then click submit, which will redirect you to the "
"@operation form."
msgstr ""
"Pilih varian, lalu klik submit; Anda akan diarahkan ke formulir "
"@operation."

msgid "Filter webforms default category"
msgstr "Filter kategori default webform"

