msgid "Translations"
msgstr "Terjemahan"

msgid "A locally hosted document, such as a PDF file."
msgstr "Dokumen yang dihosting secara lokal, seperti berkas PDF."

msgid "A locally hosted image file."
msgstr "Berkas gambar yang disimpan secara lokal."

