msgid ""
"If you want to use the Field Group accordion formatter, you will need "
"to install the <a href=\":link\" target=\"_blank\">jQuery UI "
"Accordion</a> module."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda ingin menggunakan formatter accordion Field Group, Anda "
"perlu menginstal modul <a href=\":link\" target=\"_blank\">jQuery UI "
