"dipertimbangkan."

msgid ""
"What this module aims to accomplish is the ability to quickly find the "
"module you are looking for without having to rely on the browsers "
"search feature which more times than not shows you the module name in "
"the -Required by- or -Depends on- sections of the various modules or "
"even some other location on the page like a menu item."
msgstr ""
"Tujuan modul ini adalah memungkinkan Anda dengan cepat menemukan modul "
"yang Anda cari tanpa harus mengandalkan fitur pencarian di browser, "
"yang sering kali justru menampilkan nama modul tersebut di bagian "
"-Required by- atau -Depends on- pada berbagai modul, atau bahkan di "
"lokasi lain pada halaman seperti item menu."

msgid ""
